{"tid":1902834,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【粵語分析】粵語係親泰語，多過親漢語，我哋要認祖歸宗！","createTime":"2020-02-28T14:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T06:44:43.000Z","uid":276716,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9d3e5a1f8e094ea6e3062ae879691e2825818b5a","tid":1902834,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:50:24.000Z","msg":"前post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1899529/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1899529/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原本諗住講粵語入文，但啱啱睇到啲資料，可以佐證我先前嘅觀點。<br />\n<br />\n之前幾個post我提出粵語不屬於漢藏語系，而係壯侗語嘅一員。好似呢幅圖咁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UoWg5kX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUoWg5kX.jpg&h=38b6900d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個睇法可能太顛覆，引起好多巴打爭議。但我發現類似觀點，語言學界入面都有人論證過。<br />\n<br />\n淅江嘅潘悟雲教授，佢一篇論文提出呢幅關係圖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpJvqmG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpJvqmG.jpg&h=ef1ca29a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢認為<span style=\"color: red;\">吳語、粵語、閩南語呢啲南方「方言」，係源自百越語，受古漢語影響而來。</span><br />\n<br />\n至於台灣嘅羅肇錦教授，佢就由客家話出發，得出下面呢幅圖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S2VaqmM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS2VaqmM.jpg&h=2dd2eb87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋兩位嘅共通點，就係認為<span style=\"color: red;\">南方語言同壯侗苗瑤係同一支，相對北方漢語係另一支。</span><br />\n<br />\n佢哋呢個睇法，同我觀點如出一轍。只係佢哋礙於傳統、政治因素，冇將「南方語言唔係漢語」呢個結論宣之於口。<br />\n<br />\n而我就好直白咁話畀大家聽，粵語唔係漢語，佢同壯語、泰語反而親啲。<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻，<span style=\"color: red;\">粤语同壯語、泰語係親兄弟，同漢語就係師徒關係。粵語當中大量漢語詞，係借用得嚟嘅，類似日語當中嘅漢字咁。</span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢點一日唔搞清楚，粵語入文都會有好大盲點。<br />\n<br />\n我先前個post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1884504/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1884504/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n潘悟雲論文：<a href=\"https://wk.baidu.com/view/ab87f50b79563c1ec5da7138?pcf=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwk.baidu.com%2Fview%2Fab87f50b79563c1ec5da7138%3Fpcf%3D2&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=107550b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wk.baidu.com/view/ab87f50b79563c1ec5da7138?pcf=2</a><br />\n<br />\n羅肇錦論文：<a href=\"http://www.ling.sinica.edu.tw/Files/LL/Docments/Journals/7.2/j2006_2_12_2821.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ling.sinica.edu.tw%2FFiles%2FLL%2FDocments%2FJournals%2F7.2%2Fj2006_2_12_2821.pdf&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=5122107b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ling.sinica.edu.tw/Files/LL/Docments/Journals/7.2/j2006_2_12_2821.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"a6aaa149fc89f14db2d372fa805e530cb0fa0caa","tid":1902834,"uid":130406,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n反支那攪到要同南亞人認親認戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30ada6ada1d83851bb8ca13d1efff689c840577","tid":1902834,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6aaa149fc89f14db2d372fa805e530cb0fa0caa","tid":1902834,"uid":130406,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n反支那攪到要同南亞人認親認戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bab16493b84def7dbe6a93484efb6b48b1d359b","tid":1902834,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T08:05:43.000Z","msg":"我哋要擺脫嘅係祖宗，唔係呢個祖宗。"},{"pid":"388ec959c980eebce3f359d8fa7cdb39fb82a04d","tid":1902834,"uid":276716,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6aaa149fc89f14db2d372fa805e530cb0fa0caa","tid":1902834,"uid":130406,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n反支那攪到要同南亞人認親認戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"大中華膠速速現形"},{"pid":"a2370da6891f7d67213ec87e6d1011cc8629c023","tid":1902834,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"下post: 淺談寫粵文嘅方式<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1904516/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1904516/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1c05047a8cf0f40a77b4f4f6a48abc640a832573","tid":1902834,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"完全同意粵語唔應該分為漢藏語系<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1057290560997224&amp;id=1011463772246570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1057290560997224%26id%3D1011463772246570&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=ffc009d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1057290560997224&amp;id=1011463772246570</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"a2370da6891f7d67213ec87e6d1011cc8629c023","tid":1902834,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"下post: 淺談寫粵文嘅方式<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1904516/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1904516/page/1</a>"}}